HEADWORD: Understrapper
<hw>Un"der*strap`per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A petty
fellow; an inferior agent; an underling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This was going to the fountain head at once, not applying to the
<qex>understrappers</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

